《她有名字》舞台首秀是由瓦尔德施密特执导的，他同时还负责[[景觀設計|舞台场景设计]]。<ref>For Waldschmidt's directoral role, see {{Cite news|title=Local director shines light on global crisis|author=Sara Wilson|work=The Strathmore Standard|date=January 12, 2011|url=http://www.strathmorestandard.com/2011/01/12/local-director-shines-light-on-global-crisis|accessdate=March 16, 2013|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512150220/http://www.strathmorestandard.com/2011/01/12/local-director-shines-light-on-global-crisis|dead-url=no}}</ref>亚伦·克罗格曼饰演杰森和无名皮条客，西耶娜·豪威尔·霍顿饰演妈妈桑，格伦达·沃肯丁饰演玛尔塔，丹妮丝·黄饰演18号，卡里·罗素饰演艾丽。 <ref>For the casting of Krogman, Howell-Holden, and Warkentin, see {{Cite news|work=[[Calgary_Sun|Calgary Sun]]|title=Calgary's She Has a Name a 'heart-wrenching' hit|author=Louis Hobson|date=February 24, 2011|url=http://www.calgarysun.com/entertainment/columnists/louis_hobson/2011/02/24/17398956.html|accessdate=July 22, 2012|archive-date=2017-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627181646/http://www.calgarysun.com/entertainment/columnists/louis_hobson/2011/02/24/17398956.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>瓦尔德施密特在阿尔伯塔省内的玫瑰花蕾剧院 (Rosebud Theatre)观看过沃肯丁的表演后，建议她参加这部剧的试镜。<ref name="Lethbridge">{{Cite news|work=[[Lethbridge_Herald|Lethbridge Herald]]|author=Al Beeber|date=May 11, 2012|title=She has a name}}</ref>作为导演，瓦尔德施密特得到了黄、克罗格曼和库曼的高度评价，库曼还称赞了他的舞台设计之精巧。<ref name="Standard">{{Cite news|work=The Strathmore Standard|title=Local church hosts world-class rehersals (sic)|author=Sara Wilson|date=February 22, 2011|url=http://www.strathmorestandard.com/2011/02/22/local-church-hosts-world-class-rehersals|accessdate=March 16, 2013|archive-date=2013-02-03|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130203081753/http://www.strathmorestandard.com/2011/02/22/local-church-hosts-world-class-rehersals|dead-url=no}}</ref>同样，瓦尔德施密特也肯定了各位演员的精彩表演。<ref name="CFUV">{{Cite news|publisher=[[CFUV-FM|CFUV-FM]]|location=Victoria|title=She Has a Name|url=http://cfuvfringefestival.wordpress.com/2012/08/23/she-has-a-name/|accessdate=August 24, 2012|archive-date=2016-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105042950/https://cfuvfringefestival.wordpress.com/2012/08/23/she-has-a-name/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他说，这部剧一开场就是一幕强奸场景，尽管他自己作为演员时也表演过类似的场景，但他发现比起如何去演，其实如何去执导舞台上的呈现才是最难的。<ref name="Project">{{Cite news|work=The Calgary Journal|title=Human trafficking portrayed through local theatre project: World premiere of 'She Has A Name' in Calgary on Feb. 23|author=James Wilt|date=February 4, 2011|url=http://www.calgaryjournalonline.ca/september-print-issue/arts-a-entertainment/1719-human-trafficking-portrayed-through-local-theatre-project|accessdate=August 14, 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213022928/http://www.calgaryjournalonline.ca/september-print-issue/arts-a-entertainment/1719-human-trafficking-portrayed-through-local-theatre-project|archivedate=December 13, 2014}}</ref>《她有名字》的首演是由烈焰丛林剧院 (Burnt Thicket Theatre)和公益组织“为他们发声”(Raise Their Voice)两方共同监制的。<ref name="Charlebois">{{Cite news|work=The Charlebois Post|title=Event: She Has a Name (Fringe)|date=June 12, 2012|url=http://www.charpo-montreal.com/2012/06/event-she-has-name-fringe.html|accessdate=July 24, 2012|archive-date=2012-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623151046/http://www.charpo-montreal.com/2012/06/event-she-has-name-fringe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="Sunrise">{{Cite news|work=Country Sunrise News|location=Red Deer|title=Locally Grown Play She Has a Name|volume=15|issue=3|date=April 2012|page=1}}</ref> [[基尔多南（St._Kildonan）保罗|基尔多南-圣保罗区 (Kildonan-St. Paul)]] 的国会议员[[乔伊·史密斯|乔伊·史密斯]]办公室也发文宣传了《她有名字》的首秀演出。<ref>For Smith's electoral district, see {{Cite news|title=Burnt Thicket Theatre presents She Has A Name by Andrew Kooman|work=[[Winnipeg_Free_Press|Winnipeg Free Press]]|url=http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/arts-and-life/events/161478665.html|accessdate=August 24, 2012|archive-date=2018-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922170727/https://www.winnipegfreepress.com/arts-and-life/events/161478665.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

首秀演出定于2011年2月，地点位于卡尔加里的[[艾普克藝術中心|艾普克艺术中心]]。<ref name="Strathmore">{{Cite news|title=Local director shines light on global crisis|author=Sara Wilson|work=The Strathmore Standard|date=January 12, 2011|url=http://www.strathmorestandard.com/2011/01/12/local-director-shines-light-on-global-crisis|accessdate=March 16, 2013|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512150220/http://www.strathmorestandard.com/2011/01/12/local-director-shines-light-on-global-crisis|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月23日至3月5日，该剧将在艺术中心的摩特尔表演厅(Motel stage)上演。<ref>For the location of the performances, see {{Cite news|title=Raise the curtain on a new year of theatre|author=Kevin Rushworth|date=January 19, 2011|publisher=The Reflector|location=Calgary|url=http://www.thereflector.ca/2011/01/19/raise-the-curtain-on-a-new-year-of-theatre/|accessdate=July 21, 2012|archive-date=2011-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828015100/http://www.thereflector.ca/2011/01/19/raise-the-curtain-on-a-new-year-of-theatre/|dead-url=no}}</ref>门票很快收售一空。原计划3月12日才去红鹿市进行表演，结果由于观众呼声强烈，首演四天后，该剧就在红鹿市的[[斯科特·布洛克剧院|斯科特·布洛克剧院 (Scott Block Theatre)]]上映了。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Human Trafficking – Joy's HT Updates – February 2011 Update|url=http://www.joysmith.ca/main.asp?fxoid=FXMenu,3&cat_ID=27&sub_ID=106&sub2_ID=40|accessdate=November 11, 2012|year=2011|publisher=[[Joy_Smith|Joy Smith]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722154456/http://www.joysmith.ca/main.asp?fxoid=FXMenu%2C3&cat_ID=27&sub_ID=106&sub2_ID=40|archivedate=2011-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在红鹿市表演的所有门票都被抢空。<ref name="Sunrise">{{Cite news|work=Country Sunrise News|location=Red Deer|title=Locally Grown Play She Has a Name|volume=15|issue=3|date=April 2012|page=1}}</ref>该剧在观众中间引发强烈反响，触动了许多观众的心灵。<ref name="Gauntlet">{{Cite news|work=[[Gauntlet_(newspaper)|Gauntlet]]|location=Calgary|title=She Has a Name and a story, too: Theatre performance tours Canada to raise awareness about human trafficking in Southeast Asia|author=Pauline Anunciacion|date=February 16, 2012|volume=52|issue=30|page=8}}</ref> <ref name="Justice">{{Cite web|title=Play exposes realities of human trafficking|url=http://www.ijm.ca/news/News/437|accessdate=July 27, 2012|date=May 30, 2012|publisher=[[International_Justice_Mission|International Justice Mission]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213014706/http://www.ijm.ca/news/News/437|archivedate=2014-12-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref> <ref name="Huntley">{{Cite AV media|title=She Has a Name|publisher=[[100_Huntley_Street|100 Huntley Street]]|date=June 27, 2012|url=http://www.100huntley.com/video?id=6VFfblaYp-k|accessdate=July 30, 2012|archive-date=2014-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213023137/http://www.100huntley.com/video?id=6VFfblaYp-k|dead-url=no}}</ref>库曼了解到，观看完首演的观众反应各不相同，有的与其他人讨论人口贩卖的话题，有的写信给国会议员，又或是以其他独特的方式来表达他们观看这部剧之后对这一话题的感受。甚至有的观众，一年后还会联系瓦尔德施密特，告诉他这部剧给他们带来的深远影响。伴随着《她有名字》的首轮演出，烈焰丛林剧院 (Burnt Thicket Theatre)还发布了[[反对人口贩运的组织名单|帮助人口贩卖受害者群体的各组织]]名称。<ref name="Advocate">{{Cite news|title=Play personalizes an industry that strips away identity|work=[[Red_Deer_Advocate|Red Deer Advocate]]|author=Lana Michelin|date=February 25, 2011|url=http://www.reddeeradvocate.com/entertainment/Play_personalizes_an_industry_that_strips_away_identity_116858973.html|accessdate=July 22, 2012}}</ref>2月26日演出结束之后，剧院还组织了一场关于人口贩卖的专题讨论会。<ref name="Times">{{Cite news|date=March 18, 2011|work=Strathmore Times|title=She has a name|author=Shannon LeClair|url=http://strathmoretimes.com/March-18-2011-Strathmore-Times/she-has-a-name.html|accessdate=July 23, 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029191857/http://strathmoretimes.com/March-18-2011-Strathmore-Times/she-has-a-name.html|archivedate=2013-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>
